    {
      "id": "bug1-exp-text", "type": "text",
      "x": 40, "y": 573, "width": 310, "height": 126,
      "text": "BUG 1 — Zuul Stale Config\n──────────────────────────\nRoot cause:\nRouting rules stored per-region in\na config file, not replicated by\nthe deployment pipeline.\n\nFix: Config stored in a central\nconsul/etcd cluster with cross-\nregion replication. Verified in\neach region on every deploy.",
      "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#cc88ff", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "seed": 901, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 901,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1,
      "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "BUG 1 — Zuul Stale Config\n──────────────────────────\nRoot cause:\nRouting rules stored per-region in\na config file, not replicated by\nthe deployment pipeline.\n\nFix: Config stored in a central\nconsul/etcd cluster with cross-\nregion replication. Verified in\neach region on every deploy.",
      "angle": 0, "groupIds": []
    },

    {
      "id": "bug2-exp-rect", "type": "rectangle",
      "x": 380, "y": 566, "width": 330, "height": 140,
      "strokeColor": "#ff9944", "backgroundColor": "#100802",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "seed": 910, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 910,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1,
      "link": null, "locked": false, "angle": 0, "groupIds": [],
      "roundness": { "type": 3 }
    },
    {
      "id": "bug2-exp-text", "type": "text",
      "x": 390, "y": 573, "width": 310, "height": 126,
      "text": "BUG 2 — Silent Billing Failure\n──────────────────────────\nRoot cause:\nDB migration script only ran in\nus-east-1. us-west-2 schema was\n3 versions behind. Writes failed\nsilently — no error, no alert.\n\nFix: Migrations tracked in a\nshared migration table, verified\nacross all regions before traffic\nis shifted to them.",
      "fontSize": 11, "fontFamily": 1,
      "strokeColor": "#ffbb66", "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeWidth": 1, "roughness": 0, "opacity": 100,
      "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "top",
      "seed": 911, "version": 1, "versionNonce": 911,
      "isDeleted": false, "boundElements": null, "updated": 1,
      "link": null, "locked": false, "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "BUG 2 — Silent Billing Failure\n──────────────────────────\nRoot cause:\nDB migration script only ran in\nus-east-1. us-west-2 schema was\n3 versions behind. Writes failed\nsilently — no error, no alert.\n\nFix: Migrations tracked in a\nshared migration table, verified\nacross all regions before traffic\nis shifted to them.",
      "angle": 0, "groupIds": []
    },

    {
      "id": "bug3-exp-rect", "type": "rectangle",
